name: Autumn of NFT ART - BIG NINJA ART -
description:
Autumn of NFTART EVENT! 
If you collect 3 or more works that include Autumn of NFTART in the title, you will receive a reward accordingly.

Collect 3 "Autumn of NFTART"s → 1 special NFT will be presented
Collect 4 "Autumn of NFTART"s → 2 special NFT will be presented
Collect 5 "Autumn of NFTART"s → 3 special NFT will be presented
Collect 6 "Autumn of NFTART"s → 4 special NFT will be presented

STAY TUNED!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
